\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210503/s00002/1619980186426/剛當選中大評議會常委即辭-李軒朗-已離港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210503%2Fs00002%2F1619980186426%2F%E5%89%9B%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E5%8D%B3%E8%BE%AD-%E6%9D%8E%E8%BB%92%E6%9C%97-%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=24bf90e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210503%2Fs00002%2F1619980186426%2F%E5%89%9B%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E5%8D%B3%E8%BE%AD-%E6%9D%8E%E8%BB%92%E6%9C%97-%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF&h=563a1800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210503/s00002/1619980186426/剛當選中大評議會常委即辭-李軒朗-已離港</a><br />\n<br />\n由當選至辭職相隔不足10日，李軒朗只盼校友選民體諒，若有認為其做法不妥，他亦願受批評。他又指出，評議會實權不大，改選最大的象徵意義在於兩名民主派候選人獲逾7000票，相較對手只獲千餘票可謂壓倒性勝利，「民心無變，（選舉）推遲了9個月，但結果一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到何以離港後不退選，李軒朗從現實角度解釋，若他退選，參選人只剩屯門區議員盧俊宇為民主派，意味選民將「硬食一個建制派」，該人亦可做足3年任期，但現時直至補選，其席位料懸空約3個月，「射落海都唔益佢（建制派）」。"},{"pid":"8fde1d1c6cd52e7fe3c6cecfff7d4ffe762fbb65","tid":2513863,"uid":393145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26dc6aa1863a9ea15c45658f11809b9d9cbdd86c","tid":2513863,"uid":393145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a39de4ea43f0dddb6e91c21cbcfefd7a3ef4cbe0","tid":2513863,"uid":53026,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"eed7675a3525f98bdad2579999bb5afb770c6e11","tid":2513863,"uid":23707,"like":75,"dislike":5,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"呢個post應該會有好多五毛狗入嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"五毛、一毛要搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05